  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he also told us that in his office-- and he pointed to his office to-- in that-- in those quarters that I explained before where he was living-- that in those quarters, on the desks, there are 30 revolvers with ammunition.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he told us that those of us that know how to use those revolvers should get a hold of them and protect the rest of the inmates from some stray German units that wouldn't know that the war came to an end and would still try to harm us.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- he explained that, and he also told us at that time that the warehouses are full of-- of different materials, and we should put some people in charge of it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he explained it in just those words.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of us should take charge of those and divide it equally amongst the inmates, that everybody should get his share of what is in the warehouses.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he at that same time told us that he will have to escape from here-- and by that time, we had a pretty good idea why-- that he would have to escape from here, and he would need some help from our inmates to see him across the boundaries of Czechoslovakia into Germany.",
      "word_count": 54
    }
  ],
